high_descs: Turn around and walk up to the window, then turn left and walk over to the wooden shelving unit.
Pick up the glass bowl off of the middle shelf of the wooden shelving unit.
Turn left and walk forward, then hang a left and walk around the kitchen island to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the bowl inside then close the fridge door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the bowl, then close the fridge door.
Turn around and walk towards the stove, then hang a left and walk up to the wooden shelving unit.
Put the chilled bowl on the middle shelf of the wooden shelving unit.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn and walk to the shelf on the right
Grab the bowl on the shelf
Walk the bowl to the fridge
Place the bowl in the fridge
Take the bowl out of the fridge and walk it to the shelf
Place the bowl on the shelf
anns.task_desc: Refrigerate the bowl for some time.

high_descs: Turn around and then go to the shelf on your left.
Pick up the glass bowl from the shelf.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Chill the bowl and then take it out of the fridge.
Turn around, then take a left at the stove to return to the shelf.
Put the bowl on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl on the shelf.
